  <brief_title>Comparison of Conventional Dialysis and the Allient System</brief_title>
  <official_title>Uremic Toxin Removal, Blood Cell Kinetics, and Inflammatory Response in Patients Treated With the Allient System</official_title>
  <sponsors>
